      "face": "mtn_ex_010.exp.json",
      "id": 301301,
      "motion": 1
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "哈哈……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_050.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "嗯？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你今天有点不对劲啊……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "eyeClose": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_050.exp.json",
      "id": 301301
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "哎？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "发生什么了？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 301301,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "看出来啦？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_010.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "当然看出来了呀，@我当你妈妈都多少年了。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_011.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "要是有什么烦恼，尽管说吧！"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 301301,
      "motion": 300
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "也不算是烦恼……@怎么说好呢……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 301301
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "就是感觉……不清不楚……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "不清不楚？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "eyeClose": 1,
      "id": 301301
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "就是有事情弄不清楚，有点郁闷……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_010.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "如果要解决这个问题@妈妈能帮到你吗？"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "eyeClose": 0,
      "id": 301301,
      "motion": 0
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "唔……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "不用客气，尽管说。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 301301,
      "lipSynch": 0
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "…………"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "eyeClose": 1,
      "id": 301301
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "我会自己想办法的……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "这样啊……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_011.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "唉，年轻人就是容易感到郁闷。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_020.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "不过，如果真的很困扰，@你一定要跟妈妈说哦！"
   },
