    "chara": [
     {
      "eyeClose": 0,
      "id": 301301,
      "motion": 300
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "嗯……"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_030.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "你跟你死去的父亲很像，@总是一个人扛着一切。"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 301301,
      "lipSynch": 0
     }
    ],
    "textRight": "…………"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_011.exp.json",
      "id": 800600
     }
    ],
    "textLeft": "不过，我的随性@应该也遗传给你了哦～"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "cheek": 0,
      "face": "mtn_ex_010.exp.json",
      "id": 301301,
      "motion": 1
     }
